# ---------------------------------------------------------------------------
# Pin Assignment Summary / 引脚分配总表
# ---------------------------------------------------------------------------
#
#  MOD1 (ESP32 NodeMCU-32S)          MOD2 (INMP441 Microphone)
#  ┌──────────────────────┐          ┌────────────────────────┐
#  │ GPIO25 ──── I2S_BCK ─┼──────────┼→ SCK (bit clock)      │
#  │ GPIO33 ──── I2S_WS  ─┼──────────┼→ WS  (word select)    │
#  │ GPIO17 ──── I2S_DATA─┼──────────┼→ SD  (serial data)    │
#  │ 3V3     ──── 3V3    ─┼──────────┼→ VDD (power)          │
#  │ GND     ──── GND    ─┼──┬───────┼→ GND                   │
#  │                       │  └───────┼→ L/R (left channel)   │
#  │ GPIO18 ──── BTN1    ─┼───── SW1 (Button 1)              │
#  │ GPIO14 ──── BTN2    ─┼───── SW2 (Button 2)              │
#  │ GPIO16 ──── BTN3    ─┼───── SW3 (Button 3)              │
#  │ GPIO26 ──── LED     ─┼── R1 ── LED1 ── GND (indicator) │
#  └──────────────────────┘          └────────────────────────┘
#
#  Active-Low Buttons: GPIO → Button Terminal A → Button Terminal B → GND
#  (Internal pull-up enabled, short to GND when pressed)
#  低电平有效按钮：GPIO → 按键引脚A → 按键引脚B → GND
#  (使用内部上拉，按下时 GPIO 拉低)
#
#  LED: GPIO26 → R1(220Ω) → LED Anode(+) → LED Cathode(-) → GND
#  LED1 lights when GPIO26 is driven HIGH (Button 1 pressed)

# ---------------------------------------------------------------------------
# ESP32 NodeMCU-32S Complete Pin Reference / 完整引脚参考
# ---------------------------------------------------------------------------
#
#  Left Row (J1, top→bottom)        Right Row (J2, top→bottom)
#  ┌────────────────────┐          ┌────────────────────┐
#  │ 1.  3V3            │          │ 1.  GND            │
#  │ 2.  EN (RST)       │          │ 2.  GPIO23         │
#  │ 3.  GPIO36 (VP)    │          │ 3.  GPIO22         │
#  │ 4.  GPIO39 (VN)    │          │ 4.  TXD0 (GPIO1)   │
#  │ 5.  GPIO34         │          │ 5.  RXD0 (GPIO3)   │
#  │ 6.  GPIO35         │          │ 6.  GPIO21         │
#  │ 7.  GPIO32         │          │ 7.  GND             │
#  │ 8.  GPIO33  [WS]   │          │ 8.  GPIO19          │
#  │ 9.  GPIO25  [BCK]  │          │ 9.  GPIO18  [BTN1]  │
#  │ 10. GPIO26  [LED]  │          │ 10. GPIO5           │
#  │ 11. GPIO27         │          │ 11. GPIO17  [DATA]  │
#  │ 12. GPIO14  [BTN2] │          │ 12. GPIO16  [BTN3]  │
#  │ 13. GPIO12  **     │          │ 13. GPIO4           │
#  │ 14. GND            │          │ 14. GPIO0 (BOOT)    │
#  │ 15. GPIO13         │          │ 15. GPIO2           │
#  │ 16. D2 (GPIO9)     │          │ 16. GPIO15          │
#  │ 17. D3 (GPIO10)    │          │ 17. D1 (GPIO8)      │
#  │ 18. CMD (GPIO11)   │          │ 18. D0 (GPIO7)      │
#  │ 19. 5V (VIN)       │          │ 19. GND             │
#  └────────────────────┘          └────────────────────┘
#
#  ** GPIO12 is a strapping pin (MTDI) — do NOT pull low during boot.
#     It affects Flash voltage. Avoid using for active-low buttons.
#     GPIO12 是启动引脚(MTDI)，不要在启动时拉低，避免用于低电平按钮。
#
#  Pins marked [BCK]/[WS]/[DATA]/[BTN1]/[BTN2]/[BTN3]/[LED] are used.
#  Pins not marked are available for future expansion.
#  标记 [xxx] 的引脚已被使用，未标记的引脚可用于未来扩展。

# ---------------------------------------------------------------------------
# Bill of Materials / 物料清单 (BOM)
# ---------------------------------------------------------------------------
#
#  Qty | Ref   | Part                            | Footprint
#  ----+-------+---------------------------------+-----------------------
#   1  | MOD1  | ESP32-WROOM-32 NodeMCU 38-pin  | 2x19P 2.54mm header
#   1  | MOD2  | INMP441 I2S MEMS Microphone    | 6P 2.54mm male header
#   3  | SW1-3 | Tactile switch 6x6mm SPST      | 2P 6x6mm TH
#   1  | LED1  | Red LED 3mm                    | 3mm TH
#   1  | R1    | 220Ω resistor                  | 0805 SMD or 1/4W TH
#  ----+-------+---------------------------------+-----------------------
#
#  Power: USB 5V via NodeMCU micro-USB port
#  供电：通过 NodeMCU 的 Micro-USB 接口，5V
#
#  Note: INMP441 VDD must connect to 3.3V, NEVER 5V (will damage mic).
#  注意：INMP441 的 VDD 必须接 3.3V，绝不能接 5V（会烧毁麦克风）。
# =============================================================================
